  "prompt": "How much would a wedding at a 5 star hotel in Mumbai for 400 people cost? Websites shows per-plate cost, does this include venue rental charges?",
  "response": "The cost of a wedding at a 5-star hotel in Mumbai can vary widely based on various factors such as the hotel's reputation, the specific services included, the time of the year, and any additional requirements you may have. Generally, the per-plate cost for a wedding at a 5-star hotel in Mumbai can range anywhere from \u20b93,000 to \u20b910,000 or more.\n\nThe per-plate cost typically covers the food and beverage expenses for each guest but may not necessarily include venue rental charges, decoration, entertainment, photography, or other additional services. Here are some general costs you should consider:\n\n1. **Per-Plate Cost**: \u20b93,000 to \u20b910,000 per person\n   - For 400 people, this can range from \u20b912,00,000 to \u20b940,00,000.\n\n2. **Venue Rental Charges**: These charges can vary greatly depending on the hotel and the season. It's important to confirm with the hotel what is included in the per-plate charge.\n   - This can range from \u20b95,00,000 to \u20b920,00,000, or sometimes it might be included if you reach a certain minimum spend.\n\n3. **Decoration and Lighting**: This can also vary widely.\n   - Budget: \u20b93,00,000 to \u20b910,00,000.\n\n4. **Entertainment (DJ/Band)**: \u20b950,000 to \u20b92,50,000.\n\n5. **Photography and Videography**: Professional services can range from \u20b91,00,000 to \u20b95,00,000.\n\n6. **Miscellaneous Costs** (Invitations, Gifts, etc.): \u20b91,00,000 to \u20b95,00,000.\n\nTherefore, the total cost for a wedding at a 5-star hotel in Mumbai for 400 people can range from \u20b922,00,000 to \u20b982,00,000 or more, depending on your choices and requirements.\n\nIt's crucial to contact the hotels directly to get detailed quotations and to understand what is included in their per-plate cost. Additionally, negotiations can be made and packages are often customizable based on your preferences.",
